      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>gochujang paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a bowl and mix until fully combined – this is your <strong>gochujang sauce</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
