            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>pizza base[s]</strong> to a baking tray (or two)</p><p>Brush the crust with a little <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> and <strong>black sesame seeds</strong> on to the crust – this is your <strong>sesame crusted pizza base</strong></p><p>Tip: Make sure the pizza bases don't overlap on the tray[s] to avoid raw dough!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695898242889-x200.jpg",
