            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>sesame crusted pizza base[s] </strong>with your <strong>gochujang sauce</strong>, <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong>, <strong>grated cheese</strong> and the <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the crust has puffed up and browned – this is your <strong>sesame crusted gochujang chicken & sweetcorn pizza</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
