          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>sriracha </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and your <strong>mayo</strong> to a bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p>",
