    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sesame crusted gochujang chicken & sweetcorn pizza</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>gochujang mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
